title: Coming Out On Top w/AMOS (Gay Choose Your Own Adventure)
description:
Coming Out on Top follows the story of college student Mark Matthews as he busts out of the closet and engages in all manner of adventure, all the while meeting a multitude of hot guys. Whether he does the right thing, wrong thing, stupid thing, or funny thing is up to you. Beard and body hair options available for all the guys.

Lots of replay value. Choose your own path, rewind to fix unwanted outcomes. Save and make split branches of the story!
